<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yan̊būʿu jūdiⁿ min̊ dami ạl̊fādī jaray̱
 min̊ jis̊mi yasūʿa ạlãdẖī yuḥ̊yī ạl̊waray̱
 wakulũ man̊ fīhi ạgẖ̊tasal̊
 tanaqãy̱ bidami ạl̊ḥamal̊

[V2]
 2- yā ḥamalạaⁿ qad̊ māta ʿan̊ jin̊si ạl̊basẖar̊
 hadẖā ạldãmu ạltẖãmīnu dāyỉmu ạlạảtẖar̊
 ḥatãy̱ tunajĩy bisalạm̊
 ʿarūsaka ại̹lay̱ ạltãmām̊

[V3]
 3- lamãạ rāảẙtu dama dẖalika ạl̊ḥamal̊
 dẖāka ạlãdẖī taʿayãna mun̊dẖu ạlạảzal̊
 qad̊ ṣāra ḥubũ man̊ faday̱
 maẘḍūʿa sub̊ḥī ạảbadā

[V4]
 4- ại̹dẖā gẖadā hadẖā ạlĩlasạnu ạảb̊kama
 fī qab̊rihi ạảkẖ̊rasa lan̊ yukalĩma
 tasẖ̊dū bisub̊ḥiⁿ ạảʿ̊ẓami
 naf̊sī lirabĩy ạl̊mun̊ʿimi</lyrics>
<title>ynbwʿ jwd mn dm ạlfạdy</title>
<author>Zebulon</author>
<hymn_number>5246</hymn_number>
</song>